Revision history for PERLANCAR-Module-List

0.003005 2016-03-17 (PERLANCAR)

	- [Bugfix] Make module work under perl < 5.10.


0.003004 2016-03-15 (PERLANCAR)

	- Add option: all.

	- [Bugfix] Didn't return path when return_path=>1 and list_pod=>1 &
	  use_pod_dir=>1.

	- Support 5.006 back.


0.003003 2016-01-21 (PERLANCAR)

         - [Bugfix] Don't assign to result multiple times, overriding the first
           path found (when 'return_path' is true).

         - Bump minimum perl version to 5.10.1 because defined-or is easy.


0.003002 2016-01-20 (PERLANCAR)

         - First release.


0.003001 2015-08-11 (PERLANCAR)

